videos.description: Boston Celtics head coach Brad Stevens calls Aron Baynes and Marcus Smart the Splash Brothers of Boston. Marcus says they are "nowhere near that" and Baynes says that he's heard about it, but never referring to himself.
videos.headline: Stevens calls Smart and Baynes the Splash Brothers of Boston
